  "rationale": "<p>The standard form is (x \u2212 h)<sup>2</sup> + (y \u2212 k)<sup>2</sup> = r<sup>2</sup>. Substituting h = \u22125, k = 12, and r = 7m gives (x + 5)<sup>2</sup> + (y \u2212 12)<sup>2</sup> = (7m)<sup>2</sup> = 49m<sup>2</sup>.</p>",
